dcterms:creator: S. Yun
M. Jeong
R. Kim

dcterms:description: A movie information network for node classification, containing three types of nodes: movies, actors, and directors. Each node is described by a bag-of-words representation of plot keywords, with movie nodes labeled by their genres.
dcterms:title: IMDB

dcterms:creator: S. Yun
M. Jeong
R. Kim
J. Kang
H.J. Kim
dcterms:description: An academic network for node classification, consisting of three types of nodes: papers, authors, and subjects. Nodes are associated with bag-of-words representations of keywords, with paper nodes labeled based on the conference in which they were published.
dcterms:title: ACM

dcterms:creator: S. Yun
M. Jeong
R. Kim
J. Kang
H.J. Kim
dcterms:description: Another academic network for node classification, containing three types of nodes: papers, authors, and conferences. Nodes are associated with bag-of-words representations of keywords, with author nodes labeled based on their research fields.
dcterms:title: DBLP

dcterms:creator: X. Fu
I. King
dcterms:description: A music listening information network for link prediction, containing three types of nodes: users, artists, and tags. Nodes in this dataset are not associated with any features, and the prediction targets are the user-artist edges.
dcterms:title: LastFM

dcterms:creator: C. Yang
Y. Xiao
Y. Zhang
Y. Sun
J. Han
dcterms:description: A biomedical knowledge graph for link prediction, with four types of nodes: genes, diseases, chemicals, and species. Nodes in PubMed are associated with aggregated word2vec embeddings, and the prediction targets are the disease-disease edges.
dcterms:title: PubMed
